INTRODUCTION
------------

    This software aims to privide a simple interface in a trivial game in order
    to test multiple types of Artificial Intelligence implementations.
    For more informations see <http://code.google.com/p/foxlearner/>



DEPENDECIES
-----------

    In order to run this software, you should previously install:
        - python: 2.5 or higher
        - pygame: 1.8.1 or higher
        - psyco: [optional] to speed up our neuralnetwork library

    As soon as possible we should implement other kinds of GUI, so pygame
    won't be required.



INSTALL
-------
    To run the software,
        on windows systems: "python.exe -O main"
        on *nix    systems: "./main" OR "python -O main"

    For more informations about options, see "main --help" or "main -h"



